<A>__{a blinding spotlight picks up franklin and elliot. the spotlight follows them as they make their way to the podium. franklin is hitching each leg forward, slowly. the tip of his cane hits the floor with pinpoint accuracy for balance and support. he leans heavily on elliot's arm. the walk appears effortless. he chats with elliot the whole way, still managing to flash the conventioneers his million dollar smile. but the walk is slow and the ovation is beginning to fade.}
